%% Aciklama: Read/Write veri akisi, cache, replikasyon
%% ---

flowchart LR
    CLIENT[Client App] -->|Write Request| API[API Server]
    CLIENT -->|Read Request| API

    API -->|Write| PRIMARY[(Primary DB<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    API -->|Read - Heavy| REPLICA[(Read Replica)]
    API -->|Cache Check| REDIS[(Redis Cache)]

    REDIS -->|Hit| API
    REDIS -.->|Miss| PRIMARY

    API -->|Async Job| QUEUE[Redis Queue]
    QUEUE -->|Process| WORKER[Background Worker]
    WORKER -->|Write| PRIMARY
    WORKER -->|Send| EMAIL[Email Service]
    WORKER -->|Send| PUSH[Push Service]

    API -->|Upload| S3[(Object Storage)]
    S3 -->|Serve| CDN[CDN]
    CDN -->|Static| CLIENT

    PRIMARY -->|Streaming Replication| REPLICA
    PRIMARY -->|WAL Archive| BACKUP[(Backup Storage)]

    subgraph "Audit"
        PRIMARY -->|Trigger| AUDIT[(Audit Log<br/>Append Only)]
    end
